The First Wives Club;;1996;;PG;;Comedy;;6.4;;Hugh Wilson;;Goldie Hawn,Bette Midler,Diane Keaton,Maggie Smith,Sarah Jessica Parker,Dan Hedaya,Stockard Channing,Victor Garber,Stephen Collins,Elizabeth Berkley,Marcia Gay Harden,Bronson Pinchot,Jennifer Dundas,Eileen Heckart,Philip Bosco,Rob Reiner,James Naughton,Ari Greenberg;;After years of helping their hubbies climb the ladder of success, three wives have been dumped for newer, curvier models. But the trio is determined to turn their pain into gain. They come up with a cleverly devious plan to hit their exes where it really hurts, in the wallet. Sit back and watch the sparks fly as The Wives get mad, get even, and get it all. Justice has seldom been so sweet. Or so much fun.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0116313/